            </a>
            <p>Calculate your water usage from all aspects including: toiletry, showering, bathing, washing machine, tap water, gardening, dish washing and car washing</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w3-third">
        <div class="w3-card w3-container" style="min-height:200px">
            <br>

            <a href="~/Home/WashingMachineQuiz">
                <h3><b>Housework</b></h3>
                <hr>

            </a><p>Total Water Usage in bathroom including： dish washing, washing machine and washing hand</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-third">
        <div class="w3-card w3-container" style="min-height:200px">
            <br>

            <a href="~/Home/WaterHeaterQuiz">
                <h3><b>Bathroom</b></h3>
                <hr>

            </a> <p>Total Water Usage in bathroom including： toiletry, showering, bathing, brushing and washing hand</p>
        </div>
    </div>


   
    
</div>

